T1  - Removing the Financial Performance Halo From Fortune's “Most Admired” Companies
AU  - Brown, Brad
AU  - Perry, Susan
Y1  - 1994/10/01
PY  - 1994
DA  - 1994/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256676
DO  - 10.5465/256676
