JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 1347
EP  - 1359
VL  - 37
IS  - 5
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - Fortune's annual ratings of America's largest corporations are shown to be heavily influenced by previous financial results, thus creating a halo that must be removed before these qualitative reputational measures can be used appropriately in other research. This article presents a method for removing that performance halo and demonstrates the method's validity.
AB  - Fortune's annual ratings of America's largest corporations are shown to be heavily influenced by previous financial results, thus creating a halo that must be removed before these qualitative reputational measures can be used appropriately in other research. This article presents a method for removing that performance halo and demonstrates the method's validity.
