N2  - This research combined meta-analytic and narrative review methods in an effort to assess the influence of group goals on group performance. The meta-analytic review revealed a strong group goal effect. The narrative review discusses the generalizabilily of the group goal effect and provides suggestions for designing future group goal-setting research.
AB  - This research combined meta-analytic and narrative review methods in an effort to assess the influence of group goals on group performance. The meta-analytic review revealed a strong group goal effect. The narrative review discusses the generalizabilily of the group goal effect and provides suggestions for designing future group goal-setting research.
